To cite MANTA, please use:

Maastricht antiarrhythmic drug evaluator (MANTA): a computational tool for better understanding of antiarrhythmic drugs
Henry Sutanto, Lian Laudy, Michael Clerx, Dobromir Dobrev, Harry J.G.M. Crijns, Jordi Heijman
2019, Pharmacological Research
Volume 148, Page 104444
https://doi.org/10.1016/j.phrs.2019.104444

